Actually we are probably second best, behind shamen, but granted that is arguable if you are talking about a multi pull situation.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>If one class (enchanters) can minimize enemy dps the best, and also deal it the best, this class is not dependant on anyone since practically everything they need to succeed they have access to personally. This class is then a god class, and all other classes are just a burden on them.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
