Not quite true, I need heals (lots), I need rezzes (lots), to be able to fight anywhere I wish to have fun I need at least one other pet class, and preferably two (for summoning mobs) so all of a sudden I need a 4 or 5 man group.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>*rubs temples*<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
